{"tid":1125142,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"東T製作人細谷p 最新情況","createTime":"2019-04-25T13:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T00:37:05.000Z","uid":7307,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a38ee199eb54482da686559e9aefed41ed3644da","tid":1125142,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:25:15.000Z","msg":"テレ東、不適切投稿の「けもフレ２」プロデューサーは「アニメ以外の他の部署に異動<br />\nしました」<br />\n<br />\n簡單說就是電視台覺得細谷跟「動朋2」相關的發言與文章不洽當<br />\n<br />\n現在決定調動職務<br />\n<br />\n株式会社ABC的協理川崎由紀夫更表示<br />\n<br />\n「視聴者に対し、不適切なものがあったということで謝罪しました。このプロデユーサ<br />\nーもアニメ以外の他の部署に異動しています。今はアニメ以外の業務をしてもらってい<br />\nます」<br />\n<br />\n(我為他的不當言行向大眾致歉，這位製作人已經調離動畫部門，現在不碰動畫業務)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽某隻狗講一成野都on9<br />\n<a href=\"https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20190425-00000107-sph-ent\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadlines.yahoo.co.jp%2Fhl%3Fa%3D20190425-00000107-sph-ent&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreKVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=7444fcb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20190425-00000107-sph-ent</a>"},{"pid":"9cdca152ed1af4c9f585ecf0ce25c96014691b31","tid":1125142,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:26:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a581fc11da60f8115f5f083b6643dcc64cc6c220","tid":1125142,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9cdca152ed1af4c9f585ecf0ce25c96014691b31","tid":1125142,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:26:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:27:36.000Z","msg":"一拳超人2期動畫製作人細谷伸之原因大概話one畫風得罪村田雄介<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1123795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1123795</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e03e94b22da248d64421e186dee5c47fd64a277f","tid":1125142,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:29:29.000Z","msg":"即係唔關一拳事"},{"pid":"56f720c25902fa1a72aa8be5b3e77a959596182c","tid":1125